The Gencore Phoenix is the main advanced Gencore Solo Fighter. It's an extremely reliable craft that can take a good deal of punishment.<br><br>Standard on the Gencore Solo Fighter line is the new particle redefinition technology, witch allows you to materialize extra armor on your outer hull. Pilots are warned that the system is easily triggered and that it completely drains your shields.